LAHORE, Mar 29 (APP):Punjab Chief Minister Sardar Usman Buzdar has prayed for the early recovery of the President Dr Arif Alvi and Defence Minister Pervaiz Khattak.
According to a handout issued here, Usman Buzdar also expressed well-wishes for the speedy recovery of both the leaders.
